{"tid":2070361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前谷哥CEOEric Schmidt: 華為路由器傳輸的資訊 「毫無疑問」被中國掌握","createTime":"2020-06-19T05:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T08:25:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"25c85ef0b919890e44a40e84e1cf40a8610469b7","tid":2070361,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕中國通訊大廠華為在去年屢傳資安問題，《華爾街日報》（WSJ）曾報導，華為的行動網路設備存在供執法單位使用的後門，能在網路營運商不知情的情況下取得資訊，雖然華為對此表示否認，但美國科技巨頭Google前執行長施密特（Eric Sc​​hmidt）明確指出，透過華為路由器傳輸的資訊，最終將「毫無疑問」地被中國掌握。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle前執行長、現任美國國防創新委員會（Defence Innovation Board）主席的施密特接受《BBC Radio 4》採訪表示，華為公司是國家安全隱患，且從事了在國家安全上，不可接受的行為，而施密特也很肯定地稱，「毫無疑問，由華為路由器提供的訊息，最終將掌握在中國手中」。<br />\n<br />\n施密特表示，華為也許能被視為和英國的「政府通訊總部」（GCHQ），或美國國家安全局（NSA）類似的情報機構，而要制衡華為，就是企業推出和華為同樣出色的產品和產品線來競爭。<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3201977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3201977&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2d44186c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3201977&h=3ed9f031\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3201977</a>"},{"pid":"c82ef3f4713cdf1aad3ae1f774f2f463218473e4","tid":2070361,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"你google又咁奶共"},{"pid":"f1547dabdb7f845ad275d252a4bdfed1bdf2af45","tid":2070361,"uid":275218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c82ef3f4713cdf1aad3ae1f774f2f463218473e4","tid":2070361,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"你google又咁奶共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:55:01.000Z","msg":"佢已經離開左<br />\n佢未離開前係的確反共"},{"pid":"d460bee1d53e11b40057c9a1ac0a1f646cc7bc6c","tid":2070361,"uid":176447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c82ef3f4713cdf1aad3ae1f774f2f463218473e4","tid":2